   Second suggestion is this. As a caster, if you are like me, you always have gate memmed with the exception of those times when you might have an Evac if you are a druid or Wz memed in your gate slot. Well this is one time you dont want to have gate memed. The last thing you want to do, after the raid is over without regard to it's success, is to gate back to the buff line area accidentaly. Trust me, I've done it and it could have been disasterous if I and the few raiders left hadnt reacted quickly and carefully to get me out of an ugly death loop. ( thanks again Azure and steelheart). Thats all and happy Dragon hunting.<br>
